title: Chef Style Kitchen, Attached Garages, Spa Bathrooms!
posting_body: Spacious one, two, and three bedroom luxury homes are custom built, providing residents a special retreat to call home.
The unique features in all our floor plans suit every need, including the optional attached one or two car garage.
Lofty nine-foot ceilings and a spacious, open design perfect for both entertaining and relaxing.
The chef-caliber kitchen offers granite counter tops and stainless appliances, and our luxurious bathrooms include soaking tubs and stand-up showers.
Enjoy remarkable amenities including the resort style saltwater pool with poolside grilling, state of the art fitness center, gourmet coffee and hot tea bar, and a cyber/business center.
